	The Department of Shipping invites applications to the post of Chairman in Kandla Port Trust in the pay scale of Rs.27,750-750-31,500/- (in industrial DA pattern).
	The job requirements, therefore, are the following – 
(a)	General Manageiral ability;
(b)	Experience and talent in man-management in highly unionized environment;
(c)	Experience and ability in Financial Management;
(d)	Ability to formulage and implement development plans and also to prepare broad perspective plan for developmenht of a port;
(e)	Ability ot co-ordinate with various agencies such as State Governments, the Law and Order authorities, different agencies of Cental Government such as customs, Railway, Ministry of Labour etc.,
(f)	Experiecne and ability in personnel management and understanding of establishment matters.
	Officers belonging to Indian Administrative Service who have put in not less than 17 years of service in Group “a” are eligible to considered for this post.
	The post is not a part fo the Central Staffing Scheme.  The appointment will be made for a period of 5 years or as may be decided by the Competent Authority.
	Eligible and interested officers are requested to apply urgently and to contact Under Secretary, General Administration Department, Mantralaya, Mumbai immediately. (Tel.No.022-22874955 or 22793205) for further details.
